{
  "stem": "11771.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was so embarrassing-- humiliating us-- that all the Christian kids, they used to laugh.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They're going on a sidewalk with their head up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we are not allowed to go on the sidewalk.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In normal-- in normal times, I would never-- I would never talk to these kind of guys.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they are going with their head up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now we are like second, third class, according to them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that's also was-- you know, you can live with that, when you get used to.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody used to worry somehow to get some food from the neighbor-- from the farms around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we used to manage.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "An particularly incident, I would like to point out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] The German came in from the-- first week, they came in with a list-- particular names.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took out the names.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They took out the people who were, according them, communists, or participating with the Communist Party.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They used to be employed for the Communist Party in Ejszyszki.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't know how they got the names.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My sister, Judy, the oldest one, wasn't living in Ejszyszki in this time of-- of the occupation from Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "After they took over Lithuania, she went to a neighborhood city called Lida.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But they got her on the list also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "One day, a German-- tall guy-- I don't know his rank.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I-- I don't know the German ranks, the military ranks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "German guy-- and he asked for Judith, for my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I was only-- because of that, nobody of the sisters was home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Not--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They're not-- not really in hiding.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were on different houses, like by their boyfriends, or by aunts, by stranger people, [BACKROUND NOISE] just not to be home.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
